uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:58:04.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">釣魚台 belongs to Japan!</span></span></p>"},{"pid":"409f619fdb9ac93b0231790eee28d037e3b8bcdb","tid":2322602,"uid":301479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63ed9002802bea55fcee52fe4d6312288f4d56a6","tid":2322602,"uid":237562,"like":162,"dislike":4,"score":158,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:21:27.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n<br />\n尖閣諸島是大日本固有領土"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b683fa276f6b57a4601fecbbbe931334659b54aa","tid":2322602,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"保釣號或者有其他意想不到嘅用途呢"},{"pid":"940c340bf1bf789ed96b271dfe6e748a8968a24f","tid":2322602,"uid":48067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd40270deae3355a50c89cdf072678e41a9dddf","tid":2322602,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:19:36.000Z","msg":"保釣行動人士羅堪就日前遭律政司申請破產，曾到釣魚台宣示主權的啟豐二號有機會被充公，加上船身已經日久失修，維修費高達 400 萬元，香港保釣行動委員會計劃發起眾籌購入新船。<br />\n<br />\n保釣行動委員會在2006年用90萬購入啟豐二號，船長約33米、重逾142噸。委員會每年都發起前往釣魚台宣示主權，但多次遭到大陸、港府或日本阻攔。啟豐二號 2006 年、2012 年乘載保釣人士前往釣魚島，其中 2012 年的行動成功抵擋日本海上保安廳的欄截，前往釣魚台近岸位置，7 名保釣人士成功登島，揮動五星紅旗及青天白日滿地紅旗。<br />\n<br />\n由於日久失修，啟豐二號船身傾側，船底已穿孔，船艙中部、船頭位置入水，很多位置都生鏽、圍欄鏽蝕情況嚴重，工具、雜物現已隨地擺放。<br />\n<br />\n委員會主席兼社民連成員羅堪就，被律政司入稟高等法院申請破產，案件排期明年3月10日審理。羅堪就4年前被裁定「船隻未獲允許企圖離開香港水域」及「危及他人在海上的安全」罪成，判監1個半月、緩刑2年，並罰款4000元，羅堪就表明不會繳交罰款，並會就案件提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n保釣成員古思堯解釋委員會希望拆船，他指，啟豐二號維修費用太昂貴，如果全艘船都要維修，很多已經發霉和生鏽，作用不大。但要等候明年3月10日官司法庭裁定的處理方法，視乎政府是否要充公啟豐二號。<br />\n<br />\n而現場保釣成員高叫「打倒日本軍國主義，保衛釣魚台」的口號，希望有心人能夠延續這份使命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/e787598788e3d8f375c0dc7f03039162/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201212/_2020121219385220994.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fe787598788e3d8f375c0dc7f03039162%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201212%2F_2020121219385220994.jpg&h=a88a2640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/hk/1948209</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:00:21.000Z","msg":"叫共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比錢啦"},{"pid":"68cb9a9c59c15ab47632f68eae8c5c4a2456648d","tid":2322602,"uid":48026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"洗黑錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c9d9855699ace130d2cf581f84849bdc999c9d","tid":2322602,"uid":385809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲保釣<br />\n載人出公海釣魚食沙律好撚過啦 <img src=